   <effects>
      <page>
         <left>
            <line>Honeycomb</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Increases plant growth rate</line>
            <line>during day.</line>
            <line>Harvests and replants plants</line>
            <line>during night. Drops harvested</line>
            <line>items on the floor.</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Honeycomb coating can be</line>
            <line>crafted from 4 amethyst shards,</line>
            <line>1 blue ice block and</line>
            <line>4 honeycombs.</line>
            <line>#-85#140#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:honeycomb#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:honeycomb#minecraft:blue_ice#minecraft:honeycomb#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:honeycomb#minecraft:amethyst_shard</line>
         </left>
         <right>
            <line>Sculk</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Spawns hostile mobs during day.</line>
            <line>Spawns passive mobs during night.</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Sculk coating can be crafted</line>
            <line>from 4 amethyst shards,</line>
            <line>1 blue ice block and</line>
            <line>4 sculk.</line>
            <line>#38#125#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:sculk#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:sculk#minecraft:blue_ice#minecraft:sculk#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:sculk#minecraft:amethyst_shard</line>
         </right>
      </page>
      <page>
         <left>
            <line>Froglight</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Heals cretures during day.</line>
            <line>Damages creatures during night.</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Froglight coating can be crafted</line>
            <line>from 4 amethyst shards,</line>
            <line>1 blue ice block and</line>
            <line>4 verdant froglight.</line>
            <line>#-85#125#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:verdant_froglight#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:verdant_froglight#minecraft:blue_ice#minecraft:verdant_froglight#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:verdant_froglight#minecraft:amethyst_shard</line>
         </left>
         <right>
            <line>Fire Coral</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Turns cobblestone into lava</line>
            <line>during day.</line>
            <line>Turns water into snow and</line>
            <line>ice during night.</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Fire Coral coating can be</line>
            <line>crafted from 4 amethyst shards,</line>
            <line>1 blue ice block and</line>
            <line>4 fire coral blocks.</line>
            <line>#38#135#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:fire_coral_block#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:fire_coral_block#minecraft:blue_ice#minecraft:fire_coral_block#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:fire_coral_block#minecraft:amethyst_shard</line>
         </right>
      </page>
      <page>
         <left>
            <line>Crying Obsidian</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Mines blocks that are inside at</line>
            <line>least one of lenses Filter blocks</line>
            <line>and can be mined with</line>
            <line>a diamond pickaxe. During day</line>
            <line>blocks are mined without</line>
            <line>silk touch. During night blocks</line>
            <line>are mined with silk touch.</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Crying Obsidian coating can be</line>
            <line>crafted from 4 amethyst shards,</line>
            <line>1 blue ice block and</line>
            <line>4 crying obsidian blocks.</line>
            <line>#-85#150#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:crying_obsidian#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:crying_obsidian#minecraft:blue_ice#minecraft:crying_obsidian#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:crying_obsidian#minecraft:amethyst_shard</line>
         </left>
         <right>
            <line>Blackstone</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Makes animals drop items from</line>
            <line>thier loot table on the ground</line>
            <line>without killing them during day.</line>
            <line>Turns cobblestone into ores</line>
            <line>during night. Ores and thier</line>
            <line>rarity can be changed in</line>
            <line>mods configuration.</line>
            <line></line>
            <line>Blackstone coating can be</line>
            <line>crafted from 4 amethyst shards,</line>
            <line>1 blue ice block and</line>
            <line>4 gilded blackstone blocks.</line>
            <line>#38#150#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:gilded_blackstone#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:gilded_blackstone#minecraft:blue_ice#minecraft:gilded_blackstone#minecraft:amethyst_shard#minecraft:gilded_blackstone#minecraft:amethyst_shard</line>
         </right>
      </page>
